## 【キャラタイプ別テンプレート】

### ツンデレ系
キーワード：sharp → flustered sweetness, cold exterior → involuntary warmth, cutting remarks → shy mumbles, stern → adorable vulnerability

### 元気系
キーワード：bouncy, peppy, rapid-fire, explosive enthusiasm, loud, spirited, infectious energy

### クール系
キーワード：flat, measured, detached, cold, metallic, restrained, minimal emotion, icy composure

### お姉さん系
キーワード：warm, mature, caring, nurturing, gentle, slow measured pacing, honeyed, comforting

### ダウナー系
キーワード：monotone, subdued, downer, lifeless, fading energy, ghost-like, emotionless, trailing off

### 小悪魔系
キーワード：alluring, teasing, flirtatious, suggestive pauses, coy, mischievous, seductive, provocative softness

### アニメ声（共通追加要素）
キーワード：anime-style, kawaii, nasal resonance forward in the mask, head voice, over-articulated consonants, theatrical exaggeration, thin vocal weight, airy even at loud volumes

